		<h1 class="title">阿里和万达看上这公司，就是因为它做了《饥饿游戏》和《广告狂人》？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/5/small/5.jpg?1446546855" alt="">
